\[\cos 70^\circ + \cos 65^\circ = 2 \cos \frac{135^\circ}{2} \cos \frac{5^\circ}{2} = 2 \cdot \frac{\sqrt{2} + \sqrt{10}}{4} \cdot \frac{\sqrt{2} - \sqrt{10}}{4} = \frac{3 - \sqrt{5}}{4}.\]Also, by product-to-sum,
